visNetwork 0.1.2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
  * new custom option : selectedBy, to add a selection on some nodes column
  * new option for highlightNearest : can now choose the degree of depth
  * to vis.js 4.9.0 Have a look to vis.js history !
    
